+- redsleeve default prefs
+- limited the number of CPU's for building to 2 (OOM otherwise)
+
 * Wed Aug 23 2017 Johnny Hughes <johnny@centos.org> - 52.3.0-2
 - Manual Debranding after Auto Debranding failed.
 
